<!-- ******************************************************************************************************-->
     
      <div id="rpublication">
        <figure><a href="#"><img src="docs/images/adsp.png" width="25%" alt="" align="left"/></a></figure>    
        <h3>Projects in Advanced DSP <date>(May 2011 - Jul 2011)</date></h3>
        <p class = "publicationbib"><ul><li>Non-stationary analysis on audio signals was performed using spectrogram, scalogram and Wigner-Ville distributions. Tools to analyse an ECG signal and perform
Signal Quantisation were developed.</ul>
	</p>
