      <h2>Projects: Coding Theory</h2>
      <hr>
	
      <!----------------------------------------->

      <div id="rpublication">
        <figure><a href="#"><img src="docs/images/thresh.jpg" width="18%" hspace="4%" alt="" align="left"/></a></figure>    
        <h3>Threshold Decoder for TeNet project, IIT<date>(Jan 2012 - Aug 2012)</date>
</h3>
        <p class = "publicationbib"><ul><li> Built a threshold decoder for Soft Linear Block Codes using Bossert Hergert Algorithm.
	</li><li>Built decoders for Hamming and Reed Muller codes.
</li></ul>
	</p>
       <p class = "fig">
	<figure><a href="docs/ThresholdDecoder.zip"><img src="docs/images/code.png" width="5%" alt="" hspace = "40%" align="left"/></a></figure>          	</p>
      </div>
	<hr>
<!----------------------------------------->

      <div id="rpublication">
        <figure><a href="#"><img src="docs/images/modCod.jpg" width="28%" alt="" align="left"/></a></figure>    
        <h3>Decoders for TeNet project, IIT-Madras <date>(Jan 2012 - Aug 2012)</date> </h3>
	

        <p class = "publicationbib"><ul><li> Built generic encoder-decoders for different types of LDPC codes and channels.
	</li><li>Built a generic Viterbi decoder for convolution codes.</li></ul>
	</p>
